    "data": "Dua-e-Allahumma Asleh\nاَللّٰہُمَّ اَصْلِحْ عَبْدَکَ وَ خَلِیْفَتَکَ \nO Allah! Reform conditions of Your servant and caliph \nبِمَا اَصْلَحْتَ بِہٖ اَنْبِیَآئَکَ وَ رُسُلَکَ \nwith those means by which You have reformed conditions of Your messengers and prophets. \nوَ حُفَّہٗ بِمَلٰئِکَتِکَ وَاَیِّدْہُ بِرُوْحِ الْقُدُسِ مِنْ عِنْدِکَ \nSurround him with the angels and support him with the Holy Spirit. \nوَاسْلُکْہُ مِنْۢ بَیْنِ یَدَیْہِ وَ مِنْ خَلْفِہٖ رَصَدًا \nAppoint protectors from the front and behind him, \nیَحْفَظُوْنَہٗ مِنْ کُلِّ سُوْءٍ  وَ اَبْدِلْہُ مِنْۢ بَعْدِ خَوْفِہٖ اَمْنًا، \n(those) who would guard him from all troubles and calamities. Convert his fear into security, \nیَعْبُدُکَ لَا یُشْرِکُ بِکَ شَیْئًا، \n(so that) he may worship only You and doesn't associate anybody with You. \nوَ لَا تَجْعَلْ لِاَحَدٍ مِنْ خَلْقِکَ عَلٰی وَلِیِّکَ سُلْطَانًا، \nDo not make any of Your creatures an authority over Your vicegerent. \nوَائْذَنْ لَہٗ فِیْ جِہَادِ عَدُوِّکَ وَعَدُوِّہٖ، \nPermit him to fight against Your enemies and his enemies \nوَاجْعَلْنِیْ مِنْ اَنْصَارِہٖ اِنَّکَ عَلٰی کُلِّ شَیْءٍ قَدِیْرٌ.\nand include me among his helpers. Surely You possess power over everything.", 
    "title": "Dua Allahumma Asleh اَللّٰهُمَّ أَصْلِحْ عَبْدَكَ"
}